data.title: Qatar Cities Database
data.meta_description: A database of 89 prominent cities in Qatar.  Includes a city's latitude, longitude, municipality and other variables of interest. MIT license.  CSV, Excel and JSON formats. Comprehensive database available.
data.text:
Below is a list of 89 prominent cities in Qatar. Each row includes a city's latitude, longitude, municipality and other variables of interest. This is a subset of all 178 places in Qatar (and only some of the fields) that you'll find in our World Cities Database. We're releasing this data subset for free under an MIT license. You're free to use the data below for personal or commercial applications. The data below can be downloaded in .csv, .json, and .xlsx formats.

Notable Cities: The capital of Qatar is Doha, which is in the municipality of Ad Dawá¸©ah. The largest city in Qatar is Doha, with an urban population of 1,186,023.
